********************************************************************************
                                 MCMAS-SL[1G]
  Model Checker for the Verification of One-Goal Strategy Logic Specifications
********************************************************************************

This repository contains MCMAS-SL[1G] source code and examples:
  - cudd-2.5.0-exp/                          CUDD BDD package
  - doc/installation_guide.pdf               MCMAS Installation guide
  - examples/                                MCMAS and MCMAS-SL[1G] examples
  - main.cc, include/, parser/, utilities/   MCMAS and MCMAS-SL[1G] source code
  - mcmas32                                  MCMAS-SL[1G] i386 Linux binary
  - mcmas64                                  MCMAS-SL[1G] x86_64 Linux binary
  - LICENSE                                  GNU GPL license

Note that SL[1G] specifications must be preceded by a "#PR" tag (otherwise they
are interpreted as SLK specifications).

Separate determinisation (SL[1G] optimisation technique) can be disabled/enabled
using the "-sd 0"/"-sd 1" command-line argument. It is enabled by default.

Run the executable without any command line arguments for more help.

